title: Our First Day Officially -Llen
content: Mahal i hope youd see this message, i just want to thankyou, i dont really expect it to be so early yet im happy. I wanna cry so bad, because for all things weve been through, e nandto na tayo. Maraming salamat mahal ko, I promise to take care of you, i will not leave you, mahal na mahal kita im with you, till the end i love you so so much

title: You are my 1st and 8 💖
content:
Everything is unexpected mahal ko, Imagine our first encounter is not that good. I hate you at first and hindi ko ineexpect na sayo ko pala una maibibigay yung yes and my first kiss. Even though hindi ikaw yung first love ko. I promise na ikaw ang last and my forever. I love you mahal ko, i love everything about you. 
This is our first day, and I hope and pray na kahit anong mangyari makayanan natin at maingatan ang relation meron tayo. I'm so happy na I am your official girlfriend now and you are my first boyfriend. 
 I LOVE YOU MAHAL KO. This diary will witness our love story. So let's full this diary with happy memories. 

huhuhu wag kang magsisi mafall in love sa akin ikaw tong unang nangasar eh. 

I love youuuuu mahal ko 💖

-🌻

title: Goodnight🌙
content:
Everything is normal. Kumain, naglaba, and pumasok ng school. Pero noong nakita kita ewan ko ba nafafall ako sayo lalo and narealized ko na "shocks boyfriend ko na pala talaga tong lalake na to." Apakaswerte ko for having you and naging parte ng buhay ko. You always do things for me. I'm very sorry for not doing the same to you. Sorry if I just take what you give but I don't give anything to you. Sorry for being reason why you always crying every night. I hope someday, your night will be good and have peace. If you think I am dissapointed to you because you raised your concerns and feelings. No, I am not dissapointed to you mahal ko, I am dissapointed to myself because I don't know How I comfort you. Sorry, you need to be hurt always just to love me. Sorry for being your girl mahal ko. But I will never let you go. I don't give you to others. We promised to each other na tayo na dulo. So, watch me to grow with you. Hinding hndi ako mapapagod sa pagintindi sayo mahal ko kahit gaano ka pa kadrama dyan sasabayan pa kita kung gusto mo. 

Mahal I love you and Good night 🌙 Umpisa palang ang lahat madami pa tayo mapagdadaanan na mas mabigat pa here💖
Sweet dreams Goodnight and sleep well 
~🌻

title: Quite a day
content:
Jade....... or so i call Mahal ko, My Girlfriend, My End, My Future.
This day happens to be quite interesting and also full of love.
I know na naguumpisa pa lng kami sa aming forever journey.
May mga problems na need ma addressed may mga feelings to be heard 
and may mga pains na to be healed. Love it aint easy, but to be shared 
with someone like my mahal, is to experience ease in traveling our partner 
journeys, all those memories we made mahal sobrang nakakataba ng puso
salamat sayo mahal ko. There can never be someone like you. Ill be your forever my precious Jade🌻

title: Worst day VS Him 😳
content:
Pagkatapos ng Consultation na hndi pala tuloy umuwi na ako. Then narealized ko na wala me energy, walang gana gumalaw and miss na talaga ang mahal ko sobra. Naiiyak ako kasi, i feel lost talaga and useless. Everytime naiisip ko na you become successful and so productive nanliliit ako. Mahal napaisip ako do I really deserve a man like you. Kasi You almost perfect mahal ko and super fearless. Anyways mahal, even though ganun yung araw ko and umiyak. You never failed to make me happy and feel important. 

Mahal I love youuu sorry kung hndi po kita pinayagan samahan ako ahh. I just want you to take your rest mahal ko. Mahal thank you for help mahal thank you for everything ngayon Araw also to your suprise. Mahal i am so proud to you and to your accomplishments today. I miss you mahal kooo 😭

I LOVE YOU MAHAL KO 💖
~🌻

title: Missing You🌻
content: Its kind of a sad day for me, cause im not able to see you my love but its okay, as you said magkikita pa naman tayo, but i cant help but miss you i miss your smell your face your eyes your smile i miss that sweet voice of yours, this day is full of missing you mahal ko. I knnow theres more tommorow so i better be strong. ill be heree mahal ko. Im yours always 🤍 I love you my girl!
